Logan.InTech Collegiate High School:
InTech Collegiate High School, is located in North Logan, Utah, United States, and is a STEM focused, early-college high school. ICHS serves students in 9th through 12th grades.


== Statistics ==
Grade levels (2006-2007): 9–10
Grade levels (2007-2008): 9–11
Grade levels (From 2008): 9–12.
